author: jukka
msg: TIKA-267: encrypted pdf files aren't handled properly
Only try to decrypt the document if the encryption prevents text extraction. Fixed as suggested by Sascha Szott.
Also added an input metadata key for entering a document-specific decryption password.

author: jukka
msg: TIKA-268: HTMLParser omits necessary space-characters when parsing table-data
Updated the SAFE_ELEMENTS map in HtmlParser as suggested by Uwe Schindler. Added a test case.
